database into something more useable for some PC database programs,
for those that have trouble with the original ASCII version.  Below
is the original letter that came with the script with only a minor
bit of editing.  I figure this makes as good a doc file as any.
Use the included script if you need to, and with thanks to Chris Dawson

-Mark


