Hello Mark.....

This email has to do with your wonderfull 'GHAS' database of herbs.

I personally, am not into herbs that much, but my daughter is. She is
currently studying for a degree in naturopathy at the Southern Cross
University in Lismore New South Wales Austalia. I live in a small town 
